title: The Beatles Complete
description:
This DVD contains all the Beatles albums (15) plus 
the US released Number Ones It was encoded from 
wav format straight into DVD Architect and is the best quality 
I can get within the limitations of the authoring program 
It is menu based with graphics for each album and song 
included as each song is played are the lyrics 
(got them as close as I could) 

Plus 2 songs (hidden) from Anthology

Heres a list of the albums below.

Part One.

Please Please Me 
With the Beatles
A Hard Day's Night
Beatles For Sale
Help !
Rubber Soul
Revolver
Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band

Part Two.

Magical Mystery Tour
The Beatles (a.k.a. The White Album)
Yellow Submarine
Abbey Road
Let it Be
Past Masters Volume 1
Past Masters Volume 2
Beatles Ones

Plus: Free as a Bird and Real Love from Anthology
